nodes.body: !bench

Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/ec4fce96-ff49-4f13-a6e9-3441c898bdcc) for commit 31db4ae59f446aef1056b51ad1e42ab430d05153.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/1c2eeabf-af93-4f26-bd06-cc67f558cb25/to/ec4fce96-ff49-4f13-a6e9-3441c898bdcc) against commit 26918687403e3a36cc3f2209ad2db0da46295aed:
```diff
  Benchmark                                            Metric         Change
  ==========================================================================
- ~Mathlib.Analysis.SpecialFunctions.JapaneseBracket   instructions    18.9%
- ~Mathlib.MeasureTheory.Measure.Restrict              instructions    23.7%
- ~Mathlib.Probability.Kernel.Condexp                  instructions    57.5%
- ~Mathlib.Probability.Kernel.Disintegration.Density   instructions    32.1%
+ ~Mathlib.Probability.Kernel.MeasureCompProd          instructions   -89.6%
+ ~Mathlib.Probability.Variance                        instructions   -64.9%
```
I'll have a look at these files.

This change looks independent to me; can you do it in a standalone PR?
